OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FA woman who provides social media
OL,7,Fupdates for for a rail company has
OL,8,Fspoken out about the abuse she has
OL,9,Fsuffered at the hands of angry
OL,10,Fcustomers.
OL,12,FVictoria, who didn't want to give her
OL,13,Flast name, is part of a designated
OL,14,Fteam set up to help with online
OL,15,Fenquiries for Northern Rail.
OL,17,FShe has been in the job for eight
OL,18,Fyears.
