OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "If you comment on
OL,7,Fa post or send a message it comes (to
OL,8,Fus). We see everything.
OL,10,F''I honestly couldn't count how many
OL,11,Ftimes I've been told to kill myself.
OL,13,F''I have had someone track down what
OL,14,Fbuilding I was in at the time and say
OL,15,Fthat they're outside, they're waiting
OL,16,Fand they're going to attack me when I
OL,17,Fget outside.''
