OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FOne recent message directed towards
OL,7,FNorthern on social media, shown to ITV
OL,8,FNews, read: "Hope you get cancer and
OL,9,Fyour kids watch you die."
OL,11,FIn the last four years Northern has
OL,12,Frecorded 745 public order offences
OL,13,Fagainst its staff on trains or in
OL,14,Frailway stations. Seventy-three of
OL,15,Fthose resulted in convictions.
OL,17,FSome workers who have face-to-face
OL,18,Fcontact with passengers use body-worn
OL,19,Fcameras to record abusive behaviour.
