OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FIn one such incident a conductor was
OL,7,Fphysically assaulted by a man who had
OL,8,Fbeen refused entry to a train from
OL,9,FLeeds to Manchester after he became
OL,10,Fabusive.
OL,12,FJon Ellis-Fleming, from Hull, told ITV
OL,13,FNews: "I've had threats against my
OL,14,Flife, I've had threats against my
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,F"There are times when I worry about
OL,18,Ftaking my kids out. That's when it
OL,19,Fbecomes a concern for me. When my
OL,20,Ffamily, who are vulnerable, come out
OL,21,Fonto the railway."
