OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FHe previously worked as a travel
OL,7,Fsafety officer for Northern. He said:
OL,8,F"This (body camera) got activated on
OL,9,Fevery shift without fail.
OL,11,F"I got an emergency call to get to
OL,12,Fdown to Ilkley as a guard had been
OL,13,Fassaulted and chased into the mess
OL,14,Froom. He had to barricade himself in
OL,15,Fwhile they were trying to kick the
OL,16,Fdoor in.''
OL,18,FNorthern has been under government
OL,19,Fcontrol in 2020, after the previous
OL,20,Foperator was stripped of its franchise
OL,21,Fdue to ongoing poor service.
