OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FLast July, it was issued with a
OL,7,F"breach notice" by the Department for
OL,8,FTransport for cancelling too many
OL,9,Ftrains, which required it to work on a
OL,10,Fplan to fix the problem.
OL,12,FAsked about frustrations from
OL,13,Fcustomers about the service provided,
OL,14,FNorthern's stakeholder manager Darren
OL,15,FAllsopp said he sympathised - but
OL,16,Fstaff deserved to be able to do their
OL,17,Fjobs without being threatened.
